Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:32.09,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)\c&HC3D0FA&\3c&H707DA1&}纵使待到早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.19,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}纵使待到早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:36.36,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}云雾也不会散去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.76,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}纵使太阳升起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:41.39,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}也无法看见你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:44.36,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}纵使我的世界被黑暗所吞噬
