Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:55.24,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}无法解开的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:57.64,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}满是罪孽的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:24:00.11,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}每天的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:00.81,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}请给予我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:03.12,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}那已知的今天与未知的明天的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:05.35,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}就此启程去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:07.55,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}那声音
